title: Cuban Roast Chicken
ingredients: ['125ml extra-virgin olive oil', '1 1/2 teaspoons ground cumin', '1 1/2 teaspoons sea salt', '1/2 teaspoon dried oregano', '2 tablespoons finely chopped garlic', '3 tablespoons lime juice', '3 tablespoons orange juice', '1 (2.7kg) whole chicken, cut into pieces']
